&lt;li>Adds support for &lt;code>parsnip&lt;/code> fitted models: &lt;code>lm&lt;/code>, &lt;code>randomForest&lt;/code>, &lt;code>ranger&lt;/code>, and &lt;code>earth&lt;/code>&lt;/li>
